<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa, Na thisan luonna,
 Kalvari lui dam dii diei;
 Sih thum bang ka hun zuon hi aw,
 Ka gitloh cheng silthieng di'n.

[V2]
 Ka gitloh nen cheng thienna di'n,
 Gan thi leh patsan tui chuh;
 Mang loin Na naka tui leh,
 Thisan chuh Na hun mang tai.

[V3]
 2. Samarinu khan Nang chuh,
 Kumtuonga kang theilo nei;
 Na hihzie hun helo mahleh,
 Ken Nang chuh ka hun he tai.

[V4]
 3. Kan tik ni nei talo ding,
 Lalpa damtui thiengtho chun;
 Nei silngim a nei sawpthien leh,
 Liva tui sang thieng zawng ka.

[V5]
 4. Kuole tuiphul dawn man chun,
 Damsung vangphatna a nei;
 Mahleh Lalpa thutiem lo chuh,
 Ting zolo, pehbang kimlo.</lyrics>
<title>THE BLOOD OF CHRIST</title>
<author>By Zawmpau</author>
<hymn_number>138</hymn_number>
</song>